s/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，所以望清楚合約先好簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過最後都係博炒，其實冇意思既"},{"pid":"a0b037f13cb6c634056c925fbf67f1dcd192c4e5","tid":130301,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"小事啦<br />\n11k你肯搵都有<br />\n有手有腳怕咩"},{"pid":"1ddf1a3b3eee64b6734cfc98be2c2ea2b67e26be","tid":130301,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以解釋下點樣痴痴地同時又幾好人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫我自己搵野去做，跟著我話做依樣又唔得，做果樣又唔得，然後又話我冇做野，每半個小時要同佢報一次做左D咩，日日開會，但唔係教我做，係叫我問佢問題，仲要我自己準備agenda，比本書我睇，叫我非工作時間學哂佢，每日都要有有schedule，要有好多野係上面，要比佢睇，都係工作上痴痴地，其餘其實都好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a72f75c174d62c7220a3015b7ba17dbe32df679","tid":130301,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點博炒</blockquote><br />\n所有野都hea，慢落黎，佢就已經火到爆，然後同佢講，我其實唔想做，但係唔想賠錢，都係你炒我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc66d07d5effaf4520c1957a0ae2cfb35678b18","tid":130301,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以解釋下點樣痴痴地同時又幾好人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫我自己搵野去做，跟著我話做依樣又唔得，做果樣又唔得，然後又話我冇做野，每半個小時要同佢報一次做左D咩，日日開會，但唔係教我做，係叫我問佢問題，仲要我自己準備agenda，比本書我睇，叫我非工作時間學哂佢，每日都要有有schedule，要有好多野係上面，要比佢睇，都係工作上痴痴地，其餘其實都好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有每日都要記低自己用左幾多時間做左D咩，同埋試過有一次去左半個鐘廁所比佢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2ac321be76ed85abe228e89e443deb9edb16ac","tid":130301,"uid":65424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"搵過份就解決到問題<br />\n大不了做住pt 先"},{"pid":"4856be274741eb033fccf69722f16b767b9f8917","tid":130301,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵過份就解決到問題<br />\n大不了做住pt 先</blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪比佢影響左，覺得自己冇哂社會價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋做廢人真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚自己會沉輪入去<br />\n同埋驚搵唔到...我本身經agent搵既，而家我係果邊個名一定臭哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73f893bf3f5131eb9f1d368ec68ea1e95d2c639","tid":130301,"uid":83871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:26:35.000Z","msg":"整個log mark低自己做過咩真係好 harsh<br />\n你揾過份啦唔使後悔<br />\n不過記得睇清 contract先簽啦下次"},{"pid":"1b80421847445800d86cb05426d552aa19d87260","tid":130301,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"但係你畢業第一份工 就被人炒 <br />\n<br />\n下一份工點請你呀 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0857f1f55c5c3ce27eb84e684607259ebbea3b","tid":130301,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵過份就解決到問題<br />\n大不了做住pt 先</blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪比佢影響左，覺得自己冇哂社會價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋做廢人真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚自己會沉輪入去<br />\n同埋驚搵唔到...我本身經agent搵既，而家我係果邊個名一定臭哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去GNC呢啲保健品睇舖都萬2啦 想做點會無"},{"pid":"ad40995e4a54a3bc8c44dfa71bb0536b98bbb0fd","tid":130301,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:46:25.000Z","msg":"馬死落地行<br />\n得萬一你都肯做<br />\n咁大把工都可以做 騎牛搵馬又得<br />\n依家一份侍仔都萬三四啦"},{"pid":"31a8ea98ee3a32714e2bea29afb62791ade6bdfa","tid":130301,"uid":65335,"like":0,"d